      "title": "'Gai' has given up on the candidates.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Freedom Party has decided that it will not support any presidential candidate contesting the upcoming 20th presidential election in Parliament, the party's leader Maithripala Sirisena has announced."
